dct_title_s: Carte de l'Asie mineure : contenant les itinéraires de P. de Tchihatchef en 1847, 1848, 1849, 1850, 1853, 1858 & 1863 / tracée par H. Kiepert.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Principal meridian is Greenwich, and Paris Routes follow by author are color coded. In upper margins: "Petermann's geographische Mittheilungen. Ergänzungsheft No. 20." Petermanns Geographische Mitteilungen, Ergänzungsheft N° 20./ coAcmpagne un article en 68 p. de l'auteur : Ge. FF. 5. Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is attached to companion volume.
